<h1>AUGIST (Accommodating Uncertainty in Genealogies while Inferring Species Trees)</h1>
<br>
<h4>AUGIST is a package for <a href="http://mesquiteproject.org/mesquite/mesquite.html" style="color:#009900">Mesquite</a> 
used to infer species trees by employing an objective function based on the relationship between gene genealogies and 
species phylogenies.  The approach is described in Oliver (2008, <i>Bioinformatics</i> 24:2932-2933).  </h4>
